{"tid":1043364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你會唔會做返自己","createTime":"2019-03-02T07:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T08:31:01.000Z","uid":230626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"baa350127c5a184a3fd058f7b4e9f0c95ed8a2a9","tid":1043364,"uid":230626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T07:57:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">人大左 好多時都會收埋自己<br />\n因為驚人地唔接受自己 容易喺社會上受到傷害<br />\n但係同時虛偽唔表達自己反而令到自己好攰好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"7ab5fe4240877ce662d576369c275d4ecf62a06f","tid":1043364,"uid":237362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"喺唔影響大環境同其他人之下我都會盡量做返自己<br />\n加上本身唔太在乎其他人點睇我<br />\n把口生喺你度你鍾意點講、講乜柒、你點諗關閪我事咩<br />\n我嘅人生唔到其他人理（好任性）"}]}